	&lt;p data-end=&quot;325&quot; data-start=&quot;212&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;254&quot; data-start=&quot;212&quot;&gt;To convert from Celsius to Fahrenheit:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-end=&quot;257&quot; data-start=&quot;254&quot; /&gt;
